  "instructions": [
    "Combine soya milk, flour, yeast, salt, and black pepper in a bowl.",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes until it becomes smooth.",
    "Place the dough in a greased bowl and let it rise in a warm place for 1 hour.",
    "Preheat a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add score-fat and cook until it melts.",
